dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Milwaukee_Addresses_2017. [points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which an address is assocated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which an address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed within each parcel or building.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which an address is assocated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which an address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed within each parcel or building.]
